{"tid":1396982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［水槍隊］全民瘋癲 我槍無邊","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T10:58:30.000Z","uid":216800,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94cb76cb237f79918223eca5aaff74c7e0fe639a","tid":1396982,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"大熱天時熱辣辣 周不時仲會有煙添！<br />\n為咗諗辦法幫助大家消消暑<br />\n我地仲可以用水槍黎解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手槍<br />\n後助力細，適合每個人使用<br />\n焦耳：0.002<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83h9VUZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83h9VUZ.png&h=3f4f15f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中二槍<br />\n後助力細，同樣適合每人人使用<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YQSTGS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YQSTGS.png&h=7ba310d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高達RX-78-2 改良型水束步槍<br />\n如果你係高達迷，一定會鍾意哩把野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pHWe616.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpHWe616.png&h=53a7b8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同期仲有渣古bb水槍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyBF2Er.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyBF2Er.png&h=c5e5eff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拉拉熊背彈夾式水槍<br />\n儲水量大，適合長時間作戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjKTDcR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmjKTDcR.png&h=4b82ac94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可坦可補可輸出槍<br />\n遮，飲水，輸出 三個願望同時擁有<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OCZDPfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOCZDPfW.png&h=461a5e1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然唔買都可以自己DIY<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDV7HGe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDV7HGe.png&h=23941625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然花式各有千秋，但哩支槍就唔好買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b2we68T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb2we68T.png&h=728c90ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿sir，知你熱嫁啦，幫你消消暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oPiEyRr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoPiEyRr.png&h=51890213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BT1ZyRs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBT1ZyRs.png&h=207d7c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxRVRC9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxRVRC9.png&h=bea06690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTBB點會忘記你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrbCkyr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrbCkyr.png&h=ecbb2888&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd8a2fba0464e4f290542dde384d165ec6d00fbf","tid":1396982,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d817af684f363d689041eea32338875b8b2473","tid":1396982,"uid":75156,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:35:33.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得抗爭係玩泥沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ebcdac1bdda61df9ed8d3d671b2036d11e961","tid":1396982,"uid":216800,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"74d817af684f363d689041eea32338875b8b2473","tid":1396982,"uid":75156,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:35:33.000Z","msg":"你係咪覺得抗爭係玩泥沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"畫公仔唔好畫出場"},{"pid":"013ee46b696